  "title": "Moon - Tsukuyomi [NARUTO THEME]",
  "description": "This resource replaces all phases of the moon and the moon itself in the style of the anime Naruto - Eternal Tsukuyomi (月読).",
  "body": "<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"font-weight: 400;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_b59a77ac-410a-4579-961c-c3fe870678be.png\" alt=\"x1\" width=\"235\" height=\"235\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">In Naruto, the <strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\"Tsukuyomi Moon\"</span> </strong>refers to the Infinite <strong>Tsukuyomi</strong>, a powerful genjutsu activated by Madara Uchiha's Rinne Sharingan, trapping the entire world in an inescapable dream to feed the God Tree's chakra. The term draws from the Japanese moon god Tsukuyomi and is visually represented by the full moon's light during the jutsu's activation. <strong><span style=\"color: rgb(224, 62, 45);\">Akatsuki (暁</span>)</strong>, while meaning \"dawn,\" can also be combined with \"moon\" <span style=\"color: rgb(52, 73, 94);\"><strong>(月, tsuki</strong>) </span>to signify the organization's connection to powerful celestial-based techniques and illusions.&nbsp;<br><br></p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This type of moon was used in the anime&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(230, 126, 35);\">Naruto </span>during key battles&mdash;it was very epic.</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">All phases of the moon are operational. The resourcepack is active even on <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(53, 152, 219); text-decoration: underline;\">servers</span></span>.</p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_7ef405cb-a2e1-461e-a117-20db2e4b4662.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"346\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Screenshots from game:</strong></em><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_ab9e5708-04ab-4e08-af40-95b3d306e537.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\"></h1>\n<p><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_1ad4b6cb-31cb-4069-905f-12a24b1f7bac.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"386\" height=\"292\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_30b5a545-e680-4ff0-b57d-752d89df761f.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"373\" height=\"246\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_9b001305-dcbe-41e8-a28e-b8dc450ac336.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"648\"></p>",
